converting the world into code 

write a function that acceps an array of candle heights, andreturns the number of candles your son will blow out.
input: [5, 4, 5, 3, 5]
output: 3

1. determine what the highest number withi nteh array is
2. count how many highest numbers there are 

def count_highest_candes 
  return array.count(array.max)
end 

array = [5, 4, 5, 3, 5]

array.max // will be 5
array.count(5) // will come out to be 3 
array.count(array.max) will come out to be 3